          "superpower": "The commitments you make after genuine evaluation carry a conviction and a depth that impulsive decisions never produce.",
          "kryptonite": "Waiting so long that the right moment passes is when careful discernment tips into the paralysis that costs you the very things you were preparing yourself to enter."
