          "at_the_table": "Your patient, nurturing presence at the table creates an atmosphere where the quality of play can actually be what it's capable of being. Not by being soft — by being genuinely supportive in a way that makes the whole table better. That quality of atmosphere-creation is both a form of leadership and a competitive advantage.",
