          "at_the_table": "Your instinct to include and value diverse contributions — the player who plays differently, the approach that doesn't fit the conventional mold, the insight that comes from an unexpected direction — keeps your game richer and your reads more complete than the narrower perspective that excludes what doesn't fit a prior model.",
